    <headline>Polar low, yellow level, Tromsoeflaket, C4, D3, Deep D4, E3 and Deep E4, 02 April 08:00 UTC to 03 April 06:00 UTC.</headline>
    <description>Late Saturday morning a polar low is developing at Tromsoeflaket and Deep D4 and is expected to move slowly southward. Saturday afternoon the center will be at Deep D4. West of the center the wind is expected to be northerly strong gale force 9, possibly storm force 10. The low is expected to weaken on Sunday morning.</description>
    <instruction>Be aware of abrupt weather changes.</instruction>
